text: Gunnar Lindholm (28 December 1887 - 2 September 1972) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual sabre event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1972 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish sabre fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
